<h2><code>lgBoundColumn</code> directive</h2>

<p>Creates a column that displays a read-only property from the data source.</p>

<h3>Attributes</h3>
<table class="table table-striped">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<th>Attribute</th>
			<th>Type</th>
			<th>Description</th>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>property</td>
			<td>string</td>
			<td>Name of the field to bind the column to.</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<h3>Examples</h3>
<pre highlight="html">
&lt;lg-grid model="myModel"&gt;
	&lt;lg-bound-column property="firstName"&gt;&lt;/lg-bound-column&gt;
	&lt;lg-bound-column property="lastName"&gt;&lt;/lg-bound-column&gt;
&lt;/lg-grid&gt;
</pre>